{
  "texts": [
    "Corwin, a young boy who lives in the Earth region, has a unique ability to manipulate all five powers and keeps it secret.",
    "But with the Abyssal Overlord threatening to consume all of Aetheria, Corwin and his friends embark on a journey to win the favour of the Elemental Guardians, collect the necessary artefacts, defeat the Abyssal Overlord and save Aetheria.",
    "5 Detective \"The Cipher Conundrum\" Professor Alexander Hayer has been mysteriously murdered in his study.",
    "Detective Sarah Michaels believes that it has something to do with the ancient medieval manuscript the scientist was actively deciphering just before his death.",
    "Together with her colleagues, experts and friends, Sarah solves this intricate and mysterious case, uncovering the true murder and his hidden motives."
  ]
}